Instead the method of operation is a bunch of employees bumping into each other because there is no organization to provide top notch customer service especially during this Covid19 Pandemic , people don't want to be packed like rats indoors , mask or no mask. People also don't want to wait outside for long periods of time mask or no mask either. As for wondering if your order is ready , it would make much more sense to have a scrolling screen and you can see your order number pop up when it's ready. Its mesmerizing, mostly due to the amazing, mouthwatering smells coming from the grill. The jerk chicken has a smokey taste like none other, very tender and succulent, you almost don't need the delicious sauce that comes with it. The sauce is another story.
